                        <h4 class="resource-title"><i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right fa-fw"></i> Group Psychotherapy</h4>
                        <p class="resource-description">The American Group Psychotherapy Association has affiliate societies in 31 states which offer group therapy sessions hosted by Certified Group Psychotherapists.</p>
                    </a>
