                    </a>
                    <a class="list-group-item" href="https://www.pparx.org/prescription_assistance_programs/savings_cards" target="_blank">
                        <h4 class="resource-title"><i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right fa-fw"></i> Prescription Assistance</h4>
                        <p class="resource-description">The Partnership for Prescription Assistance maintains a list of places to find coupons on prescriptions</p>
                    </a>
                    <a class="list-group-item" href="http://www.who.int/mental_health/policy/en/" target="_blank">
